parameters.content:
## ‚öôÔ∏è INITIAL SETUP
- Configure your Telegram ID for notifications
- API URL is already configured (MinhaReceita.org)
- Make sure Google Sheets credentials are active

## üìä DATA SOURCE
- Reads CNPJs from Google Sheets spreadsheet
- Filters by empty 'razao_social' column
- Processes only CNPJs without data

## üåê API DETAILS
- API: minhareceita.org/{cnpj}
- Returns +40 fields from Federal Revenue
- Updated and official data
- Includes IBGE codes and classifications
- Cadastral status history
- Free, no authentication required

## üì± NOTIFICATIONS
- Telegram notifies when finished
- Limiter prevents notification spam
- One notification per complete execution

## üìÑ INSERT NEW DATA
- Retrieves data from API
- Updates corresponding row in spreadsheet with new information

# üìã HOW THE WORKFLOW WORKS

**1Ô∏è‚É£ START:** Manual execution triggers the process

**2Ô∏è‚É£ SETUP:** Defines variables (Telegram ID and API URL)

**3Ô∏è‚É£ READING:** Searches for all CNPJs in the spreadsheet that don't have data (empty 'razao_social' column)

**4Ô∏è‚É£ PROCESSING:** For each CNPJ found:
   ‚Ä¢ Makes HTTP request to MinhaReceita API
   ‚Ä¢ Receives complete company data
   ‚Ä¢ Updates corresponding row in spreadsheet

**5Ô∏è‚É£ NOTIFICATION:** Upon completion of entire process, sends Telegram message confirming conclusion

**üîÑ The loop continues until all pending CNPJs are processed**
